  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel’s restaurant has a fantastic lakeside location and serves traditional cuisine using local produce. For breakfast you'll have a continental buffet, and for dinner a choice of three courses with a salad buffet.</p>
<p>The bar is open all day so head here for a morning coffee or a glass of wine before dinner to to make the most of the views.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
