  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Mezzolago has a great location on the shores of <a data-udi="umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ee16f6b7f5224e5c8d9b68f1d4b62c0b}" title="Lake Ledro">Lake Ledro</a>. It has fantastic views over the lake and mountains from all around the hotel. We recommend enjoying them from the lovely bar on the outside terrace or from the pool where you can chill out on a lounger all day.</p>
<h2>For the explorers, walkers and relaxers</h2>
<p>If you're here to explore, you'll appreciate the hotel's location. It's easy to get to the nearby towns and there's lots of cycling and walking trails close by. There’s also a bus stop with regular buses to <a data-udi="umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01" href="/{localLink:umb://document/8bac09b5ee37405a9498e1494235fa01}" title="Riva">Riva</a> on <a data-udi="umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ae52b40037474a3eadb1c0692c464473}" title="Lake Garda">Lake Garda</a>. After exploring, we love spending time in the hotel’s modern spa. The floor-to-ceiling windows have panoramic views over the calming lake waters, which really adds to the experience.</p>]]></description>
